sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client
    participant GW as API Gateway
    participant OS as Order Service
    participant IS as Inventory Service
    participant TB as Tracing Backend

    C->>GW: POST /orders
    GW->>GW: Generate trace-id: abc-123
    GW->>GW: Start span GW-span-1 (start time)
    GW->>OS: Forward request (X-Trace-Id: abc-123, X-Span-Id: GW-span-1)
    OS->>OS: Start span OS-span-2 (parent: GW-span-1)
    OS->>IS: Check inventory (X-Trace-Id: abc-123, X-Span-Id: OS-span-2)
    IS->>IS: Start span IS-span-3 (parent: OS-span-2)
    IS-->>OS: Inventory confirmed
    IS--)TB: Export span IS-span-3 (async)
    OS->>OS: Commit order
    OS-->>GW: 201 Created
    OS--)TB: Export span OS-span-2 (async)
    GW-->>C: 201 Created
    GW--)TB: Export span GW-span-1 (async)
    TB->>TB: Assemble trace abc-123 from all spans
